{"pageProps":{"postContent":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"我還記得第一次玩 Taliyah 的時候。","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":175},"end":{"line":11,"column":22,"offset":196}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"中路被選走了，所以我只能走上路。","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1,"offset":198},"end":{"line":13,"column":17,"offset":214}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"然後我被打爆了。","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1,"offset":216},"end":{"line":15,"column":9,"offset":224}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"我當時對她的評價是 ── 跟其他我對新英雄的評價差不多 ── 這什麼爛英雄。","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1,"offset":226},"end":{"line":17,"column":39,"offset":264}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"之後的幾個月，我在職業賽場上看了比在遊戲中看到的還多的 Taliyah，其中當然不乏一些頂尖選手，像是 Jensen, Bjergsen, Crown 等等。我也透過這些比賽建立了對 Taliyah 打法以及定位的基本認識。","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":1,"offset":266},"end":{"line":19,"column":113,"offset":378}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"日前一場 normal game 我拿到了中路，想想站樁法師我不是選 Viktor 就是 Orianna 也是有些膩了，其他角色又沒什麼興趣，選角沒剩幾秒，我想來玩個好久沒摸的 Taliyah 吧。基於前一次(應該就是那唯一一次)的經驗，我對自己與這隻角色的契合度並不抱期待。但出乎意料地，這次我玩得還算順手。事實上這樣的說法有些保守，我發現我還蠻喜歡這隻角色的。","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":1,"offset":380},"end":{"line":21,"column":183,"offset":562}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"就遊戲內來說，Taliyah 有低技術需求的 spam 技能(Q)，也有高技術需求但高回饋的關鍵技能(W)。另外，R 是一個很吃觀念但很有趣的技能，可以算是個 1/4 球流的技能在缺乏協調性的 solo queue 會是個很棒的 roam 工具。我覺得這隻英雄有其操作樂趣，跟我的打法還算合，而且有潛力成為很棒的爬分角色。","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1,"offset":564},"end":{"line":23,"column":162,"offset":725}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"就遊戲外來說，讀取完第一句語音就吸引了我的注意力。","position":{"start":{"line":25,"column":1,"offset":727},"end":{"line":25,"column":26,"offset":752}}}]},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"日が昇った…もう行かなくちゃ","position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":3,"offset":756},"end":{"line":27,"column":17,"offset":770}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":27,"column":3,"offset":756},"end":{"line":27,"column":17,"offset":770}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"這句台詞讓我對 Taliyah 的背景設定建立了良好的第一印象。她不像是去征戰，而是身負什麼重大的責任。而她並不畏懼。","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1,"offset":772},"end":{"line":29,"column":60,"offset":831}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"整體而言，我很喜歡許多 Taliyah 的台詞，並連帶地喜歡上這個角色。","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":1,"offset":833},"end":{"line":31,"column":37,"offset":869}}}]},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"タッチ！あなたが鬼よ！","position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":3,"offset":873},"end":{"line":33,"column":14,"offset":884}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":33,"column":3,"offset":873},"end":{"line":33,"column":14,"offset":884}}}]},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"あぁ！岩だ！そこも！あそこにも！","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":3,"offset":888},"end":{"line":35,"column":19,"offset":904}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":3,"offset":888},"end":{"line":35,"column":19,"offset":904}}}]},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"ただいまーっと","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":3,"offset":908},"end":{"line":37,"column":10,"offset":915}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":3,"offset":908},"end":{"line":37,"column":10,"offset":915}}}]},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"女の子には、素敵なブーツが必要なの","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":3,"offset":919},"end":{"line":39,"column":20,"offset":936}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":3,"offset":919},"end":{"line":39,"column":20,"offset":936}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"這些台詞建立了她身為女孩子且個性明亮的一面。特別是那句「タッチ！あなたが鬼よ！」真的超可愛的。\n","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1,"offset":938},"end":{"line":42,"column":1,"offset":986}}},{"type":"image","title":null,"url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WOYOXMY1Xrg&t=538s","alt":"","position":{"start":{"line":42,"column":1,"offset":986},"end":{"line":42,"column":56,"offset":1041}}}]},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"やるべきことをやらなくちゃ","position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":3,"offset":1045},"end":{"line":44,"column":16,"offset":1058}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":44,"column":3,"offset":1045},"end":{"line":44,"column":16,"offset":1058}}}]},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"砂漠にも花が咲く。まだ希望はあるわ","position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":3,"offset":1062},"end":{"line":46,"column":20,"offset":1079}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":46,"column":3,"offset":1062},"end":{"line":46,"column":20,"offset":1079}}}]},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"眼差しはいつも地平線に。そして両足は大地に","position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":3,"offset":1083},"end":{"line":48,"column":24,"offset":1104}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":48,"column":3,"offset":1083},"end":{"line":48,"column":24,"offset":1104}}}]},{"type":"blockquote","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"恐怖を克服するには、進むしかないの","position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":3,"offset":1108},"end":{"line":50,"column":20,"offset":1125}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":50,"column":3,"offset":1108},"end":{"line":50,"column":20,"offset":1125}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"這些台詞建立了她堅毅、勇敢的一面。雖然具備可愛的一面，但事實上卻是非常外柔內剛的角色。而且，她的聲音聽起來真的很舒服，還有些…親切感？","position":{"start":{"line":52,"column":1,"offset":1127},"end":{"line":52,"column":68,"offset":1194}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"所以我心血來潮去查了 Taliyah 的日版聲優到底是誰。","position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":1,"offset":1196},"end":{"line":54,"column":30,"offset":1225}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"該說我內心早就猜到了嗎？","position":{"start":{"line":56,"column":1,"offset":1227},"end":{"line":56,"column":13,"offset":1239}}}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"image","title":"","url":"the-stone_1.png","alt":"TODO"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"我的下一隻 main 就是 Taliyah。","position":{"start":{"line":60,"column":1,"offset":1263},"end":{"line":60,"column":23,"offset":1285}}}]}],"postSummary":{"id":"the-stone","title":"The Stone","category":"Leauge of Legends","language":["zh-TW"],"tags":["坂本真綾"],"publishDate":"2017-05-01","pathname":"the-stone","zhTwLink":null,"filename":"The Stone (blog)"}},"__N_SSG":true}